name: Degen Trash Panda #10441
description: The rarest of Pit the Panda's Trash Trap game items, the Juice Box, was minted by 35 lucky Trash Pandas. Those Pandas banded together as the JuiceDAO and diamond-handed their juices in spite of the temptation to throw them away. As a reward for their loyalty, the Pandas were bestowed an entanglement, so that they could forever taste the sweet Ape-le Juice of victory.
